These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, pineapple, pomegranate
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, aquamarine, light-blue
1. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes emerald is on the left or right of the person who likes light-blue##3
3. the person who likes emerald is the person eating pineapple##1
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes aquamarine is the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | pomegranate | cauliflower | pineapple |
| Color    | aquamarine    | light-blue | emerald |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking
House: gothic-revival, victorian, modern
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
2. the victorian house is in an even position##4
3. the modern house is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the victorian house is the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | drawing | filmmaking | board-games |
| House   | modern    | victorian     | gothic-revival        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, sudoku
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, alhambra, ritmeester
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the oliveros-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | photography | baking |
| Cigar   | alhambra | oliveros     | ritmeester  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, superhero
3 different games are played: snooker, whist, domino
1. the person watching sports movies is the person playing whist##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the person playing domino##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports  | musical  |
| Game         | snooker  | whist | domino |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
There 3 different types of food: cauliflower, kiwi, lime
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, dutch
1. the person eating lime is between the person eating cauliflower and the canadian##2
2. the person eating kiwi is in an odd position##4
3. the dutch is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Food         | cauliflower   | lime | kiwi    |
| Nationality   | colombian | dutch     | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, airplane, boat
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person driving the airplane##1
3. the person driving the airplane is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Transport   | airplane | boat | jet-ski   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, ebony, green
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle
1. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who likes white##1
2. the person who likes white is between the owner of the turtle and the person who likes green##2
3. the person who likes white is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Color   | green | white | ebony |
| Pet           | goat         | dog         | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, carrot, kale
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, sports, drama
1. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching sports movies and the person eating artichoke##2
2. the person watching drama movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person eating kale##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | carrot | kale | artichoke |
| Movie-Genre    | sports    | epic | drama     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: puzzles, filmmaking, rock-climbing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: climbing, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who's sport is tennis is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing   | filmmaking  | puzzles  |
| Sport         | tennis | lacrosse | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, mystery, scientific
1. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola      | coffee |
| Movie-Genre       | mystery | scientific | spy   |

