The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skiing, swimming, rowing
1. the teacher is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is the journalist##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is the teacher##1
4. the teacher is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | lawyer | teacher | journalist |
| Sport   | swimming | rowing   | skiing |

