.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
House: cape-cod, gothic-revival, wooden
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the wooden house is between the gothic-revival house and the owner of the pony##2
2. the gothic-revival house is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the wooden house is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| House   | gothic-revival | wooden | cape-cod |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
City: hamburg, paris, prague
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz
1. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
4. the person traveling to prague is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| City   | hamburg  | prague     | paris |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

