.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-16::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, kale, watermelon
3 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is the person eating watermelon##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
3. the person playing backgammon is in an odd position##4
4. the person playing billiard is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Food          | watermelon | cucumber | kale  |
| Game   | mah-jongg      | billiard  | backgammon |

