.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: weightlifting, rugby, biathlon
3 different pets are kept: hamster, pony, turtle
1. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the hamster is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |
| Sport   | weightlifting | biathlon | rugby    |
| Pet           | pony     | turtle  | hamster |

