.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  doctor, coach, security-guard
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, jazz
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the doctor##1
2. the doctor is in the middle##1
3. the security-guard is the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Job         | security-guard | doctor   | coach |
| Music-Genre   | funk   | classical | jazz      |

