2. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4
3. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Flower      | daisy | orchid | iris |
